{"tid":917222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嘈左成日泛民支持者都係得一個論點","createTime":"2018-11-26T09:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T11:01:40.000Z","uid":27446,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"db62ce38ddca217d3080a4c1d578324db5598f75","tid":917222,"uid":27446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:12:37.000Z","msg":"就係你地應該含撚投票<br />\n<br />\n我睇到泛民支持者既言論大概有幾款：<br />\n1.焦土派咁搞法就係放水比中共<br />\n2.兩害取其輕<br />\n3.唔係睇想投比邊個而應該係睇唔想比邊個入<br />\n4.搞死泛民又唔會傷到中共/建制<br />\netc.<br />\n所以就應該投泛民<br />\n<br />\n睇左咁多個post全部泛民支持者都係講緊唔投泛民有咩後果<br />\n但係冇一個講得出投左泛民有乜好<br />\n比佢入到去做到乜<br />\n換句話就係為大局你應該含撚<br />\n<br />\n連班支持者除左含撚之外都搵唔到其他理由投泛民<br />\n你叫人點撐你"},{"pid":"3d1cdd7c30d466983b88edd261102302ec46101c","tid":917222,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:16:25.000Z","msg":"落左選都仲可以屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n保皇狗依加搶到關鍵一席<br />\n佢推賣港政策時你有咩具體方法懲罰佢地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db1034f0e4a2de00aa425c3a36756d1c46c9923","tid":917222,"uid":27446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d1cdd7c30d466983b88edd261102302ec46101c","tid":917222,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:16:25.000Z","msg":"落左選都仲可以屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n保皇狗依加搶到關鍵一席<br />\n佢推賣港政策時你有咩具體方法懲罰佢地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:21:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"301002fa1efa04a5045a3072eda4053b365f8e85","tid":917222,"uid":38194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3d1cdd7c30d466983b88edd261102302ec46101c","tid":917222,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T09:16:25.000Z","msg":"落左選都仲可以屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n保皇狗依加搶到關鍵一席<br />\n佢推賣